<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
<tr>
	<td width="1%">&nbsp;</td>
	<td width="98%">
  
		<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
		<tr>
		    <td valign="top">
		     <p><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Article Title:</b>&nbsp;</font>
		     <font face="Verdana" size="2">-= Halloween GM Event, All you want to know =-</font><br>
		     <a href = "../Subscribe.asp?DID=514772" ><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></p>
			 </td>
		</tr>
		
		<tr><td>&nbsp;</tr><tr>
		
		    <td valign="top"><div style= "padding:4;float: right"> <script language=JavaScript src=http://www.obsidian-tech.com/absolutebm/abmx.aspx?z=26></script></div><p><font face="Verdana" size="2">
		    <blockquote>
  <p>I made this topic because I checked all the other news and they all looked incomplete so I'll make it short and informative.<br>
  <br>
  I hunted during the past 2 days with my Warrior(37)and druid(32) in Qeynos Hills, East Karana, West Commonlands and Rathe Mountains and here is my complete list of observations.<br>
  <br>
  Qeynos Hills : Many Skeletons, many kinds...best drop i heard of was Opal (worth 15pp) but they usually drop rusty weapons. The mobs were mostly low-level (10 or so) but some mob were around 20-25. Not worth the travel.<br>
  <br>
  East Karana : Best of all the zones if you are not strong enough to survive in Rathe Mountains. The mobs are specters, ghouls, spiders, evil eyes, gnolls and all Lvl 37 or lower and they give great stuff...i dont know all the items stats but I know all items that drop there and they are reported below.<br>
  <br>
  West Commonlands: Werewolves but not everywhere...this event was not so bad but the werewolves were outnumbered 10 to 1 !!! ...there was so many players in this zone that you keep get KSed and its real hard to loot or kill something. But, some stuff drop especially in WC and nowhere else...check the list at the end.<br>
  <br>
  Rathe Mountain: This zone is for high-level char...good thinking Verant...you though that you would free EK and WC of the high-levels by sending them in RM..but guess again...Hi-levels were in every zone and KSing a lot...i went in RM just to receive a 500 dmg area-effect blast and then I left. Many players in my guild went there and it dropped real good bard stuff and a caster robe, 9ac, 9int....many other items probably but i dont know anything more.<br>
  <br>
  Item List !!<br>
  <br>
  There is a * on items that drop only in WC or mostly in WC and ** on items only in RM or mostly.<br>
  <br>
  - Real Rare Drop<br>
  + Rare Drop<br>
  ++ Normal Drop<br>
  +++ Common Drop<br>
  <br>
  -Sword: 1HS, 12 26, 3str, 3sta, procs 176dd, WAR<br>
  -Sword: ????, SHD<br>
  +Mace: 1HB, 13 26, 5str, procs 110dd, BRD<br>
  +Dagger: ????, ROG*<br>
  ++Shield: ???, PAL<br>
  -Robe: 9ac, 9int plus resist, NEC/WIZ/ENC/MAG**<br>
  +++Cloak: ????, RNG&nbsp;<br>
  +++Cloak: ????, NEC/WIZ/ENC/MAG<br>
  ++Cloak: ????, ROG<br>
  ++Cloak: ????, SHD<br>
  ++Shoulders: ???? ROG<br>
  ++Shoulders: ????, MNK<br>
  +Shoulders: ????, BRD<br>
  ++Shoulders: ????, PAL<br>
  ++Gloves: ????, ROG<br>
  +Boots: ????, MNK<br>
  +Boots: ????, RNG<br>
  -Neck: 4ac, 4str, 10sv all, WAR<br>
  ++Neck: ????, PAL<br>
  +++Neck: 15mana, 15hp and some resist, CLR/DRU/SHM<br>
  ++Wrist: ????, BRD<br>
  ++Wrist: ????, NEC/WIZ/ENC/MAG<br>
  +Wrist: 8ac, 5str, 15hp, WAR*<br>
  ++Wrist: ????, NEC/WIZ/ENC/MAG<br>
  +++Face: 4ac, 4str, 7cha, 5sv magic, BRD<br>
  ++Face: ????, SHD<br>
  -Face: 10ac, 20hp and resists, MNK<br>
  +++Head: 10ac, 3agi, 3dex, 3str, WAR<br>
  ++Head: 4ac, 4wis, 4mana, 4sv magic, DRU<br>
  ++Head: 2ac, 1wis, 1str, 2sta or close, DRU*<br>
  -Ear: 5ac, low haste (has to be confirmed), WAR*<br>
  +Ear: ????, MNK*<br>
  ++Ear: ????, RNG*<br>
  +Ear: 1ac, 4wis, 20mana, 20hp, DRU*<br>
  -Ring: Was not able to loot it or get stats, WAR*<br>
  ++Ring: 2ac, +3 to 3stats, BRD*<br>
  +++Ring: 3ac, 3int, 30mana, NEC/WIZ/ENC/MAG<br>
  -Belt: ????, NEC/WIZ/ENC/MAG<br>
  +Belt: 6ac, 6wis, 6sta, 5sv magic, CLR/DRU/SHM<br>
  +Belt: 10ac, 6str, 3sta, 3svcold, 3svmagic, WAR<br>
  -Belt: ????, MNK<br>
  <br>
  There is more items, I cant remember all but it was a very big frenzy and it still is. Get all your items for your class before the event goes out ! ...I am 95% sure for the item list so some items in there might be inexistant...especially for Rogue and Shadowknights...i dont remember well their drop but i did my best...I hope this helps !<br>
  <br>
  Happy Halloween !<br>
  <br>
  Kaerdon Winterblaze and Krugen Woodshaper<br>
  Lvl 37 warrior and Lvl 32 druid<br>
  Quelious Server</p>
</blockquote>

		    </font></p>
