A quest mob says &quot;It's Humans like you who have ruined your own lands. You'll not ruin mine!!&quot;<BR>
<BR>
Quest mob hits YOU for 15 damage.<BR>
You slash a quest mob for 12 damage.<BR>
You kick a quest mob for 7 damage.<BR>
A quest mob hits YOU for 18 damage.<BR>
You slash a quest mob for 9 damage.<BR>
You pierce a quest mob for 12 damage.<BR>
Killstealer crushes a quest mob for 80 damage.<BR>
You say &quot;On him&quot;<BR>
Killstealer crushes a quest mob for 72 damage.<BR>
You say &quot;ON HIM&quot;<BR>
You slash a quest mob for 8 damage.<BR>
Killstealer crushes a quest mob for 69 damage.<BR>
You say &quot;STOP KSING&quot;<BR>
You slash a quest mob for 15 damage.<BR>
Killstealer crushes a quest mob for 81 damage.<BR>
Killstealer has slain a quest mob.<BR>
** Killstealer immediately loots the quest mob and runs off saying nothing, as if nothing had happened, and you were not significant enough to give even a /rude. **<BR>
<BR>
THAT's what was happening in WC yesterday.  It doesn't matter if there were 20 or 200 people in the zone, that's not right.  <BR>
